List of required libraries:

i) OpenCV
ii) Directfb
iii) Boost
iv) Onion 
v) librsvg2 

================================================================

Installation on Debian based systems. (State Oct 2012 )

----------------------------------------------------------------
i) sudo apt-get install libopencv-core-dev libopencv-highgui-dev
ii) sudo apt-get install libdirectfb-dev
iii) sudo apt-get install libboost-signals-dev libboost-iostreams-dev libboost-system-dev
iv) This lib has to be installed manually.
	I.e.:
	cd TinyPrint
	git clone https://github.com/davidmoreno/onion.git
	cd onion
	mkdir build
	cd build
	cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=../../lib/onion ..
	make
	make install

v) sudo apt-get install librsvg2-dev 
